reviewText: Quick service. Product exactly as promised.
4 great movies for one low price. Can't beat it.
Gift for grown son. Loves all the movies. A good pack.
SO GREAT. Came promptly and was great quality. I ordered this because my roommate hadn't seen Men in Tights. Now she has and we get the bonus of the three other films.
Great mix of movies. Exactly what I was expecting.

4 amazing movies 1 amazing price!
BUY! BUY! BUY!
Arrived as stated. I ordered it for "Grandma's Boy" &  "Super Troopers". Well worth the price, and the best price online for a new DVD of this kind!
Gave it as a gift and haven't heard anything bad, so will assume it was good
